msgstr "Canvieu la vostra contrasenya."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   [[!toggle id=\"4_ps_passphrase\" text=\"Display the instructions to change the passphrase of your Persistent Storage.\"]]\n"
msgstr "   [[!toggle id=\"4_ps_passphrase\" text=\"Mostra les instruccions per canviar la contrasenya del vostre Emmagatzematge Persistent.\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   [[!toggleable id=\"4_ps_passphrase\" text=\"\"\"\n"
msgstr "   [[!toggleable id=\"4_ps_passphrase\" text=\"\"\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   [[!inline pages=\"security/argon2id/ps_passphrase.inline\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"
msgstr "   [[!inline pages=\"security/argon2id/ps_passphrase.inline.ca\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"If you created your Persistent Storage with Tails 5.12 or earlier, we "
"recommend you migrate your entire Tails to a different USB stick and destroy "
"your old Tails USB stick (or at least [[securely delete the entire device|"
"doc/encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion#device]])."
msgstr ""
"Si vau crear el vostre Emmagatzematge Persistent amb Tails 5.12 o anterior, "
"us recomanem que migreu tot el vostre Tails a un llapis USB diferent i "
"destruïu el vostre antic llapis USB de Tails (o almenys [[elimineu de manera "
"segura tot el dispositiu|doc/encryption_and_privacy/"
"secure_deletion#device]])."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   If you don't, the previous LUKS1 data might still be written in some recovery\n"
"   data on the USB stick and could be recovered using advanced data forensics\n"
"   techniques.\n"
msgstr ""
"   Si no ho feu, és possible que les dades anteriors de LUKS1 encara estiguin\n"
"   escrites en algunes dades de recuperació al llapis USB i es podrien recuperar\n"
"   mitjançant tècniques avançades d'anàlisi forense de dades.\n"

#. type: Plain text
