#. type: Title ###
#, no-wrap
msgid "Backup Tails (4 words or fewer)"
msgstr "Còpia de seguretat de Tails (4 paraules o menys)"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To secure your [[backup Tails|doc/persistent_storage/backup]], if you have "
"one:"
msgstr ""
"Per protegir la vostra [[còpia de seguretat de Tails|doc/persistent_storage/"
"backup]], si en teniu:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Start on your main Tails USB stick."
msgstr "Comenceu al vostre llapis USB principal de Tails."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Update your main Tails USB stick to Tails 5.14."
msgstr "Actualitzeu el vostre llapis USB principal de Tails a Tails 5.14."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Create a new backup Tails using *Tails Cloner*"
msgstr "Creeu una nova còpia de seguretat de Tails amb el *Clonador de Tails*"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   If you created your Persistent Storage with Tails 5.12 or earlier, we\n"
"   recommend you create your new backup Tails on a different USB stick and\n"
"   destroy your old backup Tails (or at least [[securely delete the entire\n"
"   device|doc/encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion#device]]).\n"
msgstr ""
"   Si heu creat el vostre Emmagatzematge Persistent amb Tails 5.12 o anterior,\n"
"   us recomanem que creeu la vostra nova còpia de seguretat de Tails en un llapis USB diferent i\n"
"   destruïu les vostres còpies de seguretat anteriors de Tails (o almenys [[suprimiu de manera segura tot\n"
"   el dispositiu|doc/encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion#device]]).\n"

