"un SSD) o no us sentiu còmode amb la línia d'ordres:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"If you created your encrypted volume with Tails 5.13 or later, we recommend "
"you change your passphrase."
msgstr ""
"Si heu creat el vostre volum encriptat amb Tails 5.13 o posterior, us "
"recomanem que canvieu la contrasenya."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  Follow our instructions on [[changing the passphrase of an existing encrypted\n"
"  partition|doc/encryption_and_privacy/encrypted_volumes#changing]].\n"
msgstr ""
"  Seguiu les nostres instruccions sobre com [[canviar la contrasenya d'una partició encriptada\n"
"  existent|doc/encryption_and_privacy/encrypted_volumes#changing]].\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"If you created your encrypted volume with Tails 5.12 or earlier, we "
"recommend you migrate all your encrypted data to a new encrypted device."
msgstr ""
"Si heu creat el vostre volum encriptat amb Tails 5.12 o anterior, us "
"recomanem que migreu totes les vostres dades encriptades a un nou dispositiu "
"encriptat."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  Follow our instructions on [[creating and using LUKS encrypted\n"
"  volumes|doc/encryption_and_privacy/encrypted_volumes]].\n"
